# Arquitetura do Framework CLIP

O projeto utiliza o padrão de projeto **Factory Method** para desacoplar a lógica de ingestão de dados do processamento central.

```mermaid
classDiagram
    class CLIPService {
        +Config config
        +Scheduler scheduler
        +iniciar()
        +setup_logging()
    }

    class ConnectorFactory {
        +get_connector(type, params) BaseConnector
    }

    class BaseConnector {
        <<abstract>>
        +dict params
        +fetch_data()*
        +transform_to_json()*
        +send_to_rabbit()
    }

    class CSVConnector {
        +fetch_data()
        +transform_to_json()
    }

    class APIConnector {
        +fetch_data()
        +transform_to_json()
    }

    class DBConnector {
        +fetch_data()
        +transform_to_json()
    }

    CLIPService --> ConnectorFactory : solicita conector
    ConnectorFactory ..> BaseConnector : cria
    BaseConnector <|-- CSVConnector : implementa
    BaseConnector <|-- APIConnector : implementa
    BaseConnector <|-- DBConnector : implementa
    CLIPService o-- BaseConnector : gerencia execução
